title: #92Noon at TCO: Zimmer / Warren / Birk / Jordan / Wobby
description:
The FAN's Paul Allen is live from the TCO Performance Center in Eagan with a great group of guests:

Vikings COO and future Big Ten Commissioner Kevin Warren, former Vikings center and Super Bowl champion Matt Birk, former Vikings TE Steve Jordan, and Vikings.com's Mike Wobschall.
